    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car runs well, you can expect some noticeable cosmetic wear, including minor dents and interior staining. It is mechanically sound for daily commutes, though it may eventually require routine maintenance for older components. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
