    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint still shows a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with only slight bolsters wear on the driver's seat and minor scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and all features are fully functional, making it a dependable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 33000.0,
